^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now let me discuss New Minor Forcing and its variants. Basic New Minor Forcing works as follows. Partner opens 1 of a minor, you respond 1 of a major and partner rebids 1N (or 2N). If you then bid the other minor (2@D on this hand because Ruth opened 1@C) that is completely artificial. It asks the 1N bidder about the major suit holdings and says nothing about the bid minor. |
