NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The 1N bidder has 4 choices.

First choice is to show 3-card support for responder's major (if opener had 4-card support they would have raised immediately). On this hand Ruth's first obligation is to show 3-card spade suit (with 4 spades she would have bid 2@S instead of 1N).|
